00:14:47,875 --> 00:14:52,575
Not knowing what else to do,
when the tree eventually
bore fruits,

239
00:14:52,675 --> 00:14:59,642
I forbid my pupils to eat them,
But Chinpu and Mingetsu
disobeyed me.

240
00:14:59,742 --> 00:15:02,742
Two clones were created,
and without knowing it,

241
00:15:02,842 --> 00:15:05,875
they served the fruit to
us, and we wound up here.

242
00:15:06,975 --> 00:15:08,542
[Mingetsu] Think you can
defeat us...

243
00:15:08,642 --> 00:15:10,275
[Chinpu] ...in your
current state?

244
00:15:10,375 --> 00:15:13,742
[Goku] Shut up! Will you please
stand still?!

245
00:15:13,842 --> 00:15:16,575
His movements have grown
quite sluggish.

246
00:15:16,675 --> 00:15:20,242
We might still have to wait
a while before he becomes
a bulb.

247
00:15:20,342 --> 00:15:22,542
It's time for the next step.

248
00:15:22,642 --> 00:15:25,042
Yes, we may have to use these.

249
00:15:25,142 --> 00:15:27,042
What are those? Weapons?!

250
00:15:27,142 --> 00:15:28,909
No, these are tools.

251
00:15:29,009 --> 00:15:30,209
A kingekishi...

252
00:15:30,309 --> 00:15:31,942
...and tanban.

253
00:15:32,042 --> 00:15:33,275
[Hakkai] Hold it a second.

254
00:15:33,375 --> 00:15:36,742
Where did you say Mingetsu
and Chinpu come from?

255
00:15:36,842 --> 00:15:39,375
[Gosoukan] They are
ninjinka fruits.

256
00:15:39,475 --> 00:15:42,375
It steals people's genetic codes

257
00:15:42,475 --> 00:15:46,209
The grows an exact duplicate out
of their seeds.

258
00:15:46,309 --> 00:15:48,609
Identical replicas.

259
00:15:50,542 --> 00:15:53,175
They're clones.

260
00:15:53,275 --> 00:15:56,342
When Goku and Lirin tried to
pick those fruits they...

261
00:15:56,442 --> 00:16:00,542
It took a sample when they were
pricked by the ninjinka vines.

262
00:16:00,642 --> 00:16:05,009
[Sanzo] If that's the case, then
even he may havemet his match.

263
00:16:06,142 --> 00:16:07,409
[Goku] What?!

264
00:16:07,509 --> 00:16:09,642
[Chinpu] If we had allowed her
to fully ripen,

265
00:16:09,742 --> 00:16:12,375
she would have become conscious
like us.

266
00:16:17,542 --> 00:16:19,709
[Mingetsu] But her powers are
the same as the real thing!

267
00:16:19,809 --> 00:16:21,242
She should defeat you!

268
00:16:21,342 --> 00:16:25,275
Hey, lay off of me and let's
get to the real root of
the problem!

269
00:16:31,242 --> 00:16:32,342
Bitch!

270
00:16:38,542 --> 00:16:41,442
You're not nearly as cute as
the real one!

271
00:16:47,142 --> 00:16:48,309
Damn him!

272
00:16:48,409 --> 00:16:51,175
Let's see if he fights as well
against large numbers!

273
00:17:00,209 --> 00:17:02,675
Uh, this isn't good.

274
00:17:02,775 --> 00:17:05,675
[Chinpu] No one can be stronger
than themselves.

275
00:17:05,775 --> 00:17:08,975
[Mingetsu] Will you give up now
and become a pod-person?

276
00:17:13,742 --> 00:17:15,309
It's finally sprouted.

277
00:17:15,409 --> 00:17:17,409
Yes, let's seize him!

278
00:17:17,509 --> 00:17:18,575
[Sanzo] Stop!

279
00:17:22,775 --> 00:17:26,409
Sheesh, I thought one Goku was
bad enough.

280
00:17:26,509 --> 00:17:29,675
You should think of all the
trouble they'll cause
other folks.

281
00:17:29,775 --> 00:17:33,075
Besides, illegal copies are an
infringement of copyright.

282
00:17:33,175 --> 00:17:38,142
S-Sanzo... Gojyo... Hakkai...

283
00:17:38,275 --> 00:17:40,809
We knew you guys would come
back here for your friend.

284
00:17:40,909 --> 00:17:43,509
You saved us the trouble of
chasing after you.

285
00:17:43,609 --> 00:17:46,542
So these guys must be
Kougaiji's assassins?

286
00:17:46,642 --> 00:17:50,442
His own sister has become root
bait. I find that unlikely.

287
00:17:50,542 --> 00:17:54,642
In that case, then it's the
mastermind who's pulling all
of Kougaiji's strings.

288
00:17:54,742 --> 00:17:59,375
That makes sense. The twisted
personalities seem to point in
that direction.

289
00:17:59,475 --> 00:18:01,309
Ha! Useless babble.

290
00:18:01,409 --> 00:18:02,542
Kill at will.

291
00:18:04,242 --> 00:18:05,909
Now you're composte heap.

292
00:18:08,742 --> 00:18:12,975
Ha! I like this. Beating up
a gang of monkeys feels
pretty good!

293
00:18:13,075 --> 00:18:17,575
[Hakkai chuckles] I know it's
hard, but do try not to destroy
the original, will you?

294
00:18:19,309 --> 00:18:23,142
For some reason, it bothers me
they're having this much fun
defeating me!

295
00:18:23,242 --> 00:18:25,275
Just whose side are they
on anyway!

296
00:18:25,375 --> 00:18:26,942
[Mingetsu] What?!
[Chinpu] I don't understand!

297
00:18:27,042 --> 00:18:28,942
They should have the same
powers as Goku!

298
00:18:29,042 --> 00:18:32,609
Don't underestimate us. Goku may
be nutty but he ain't no fruit!

299
00:18:32,709 --> 00:18:35,475
The Goku we know is much
more daft!

300
00:18:39,842 --> 00:18:42,709
Next time you take a DNA sample
from Goku,

301
00:18:42,809 --> 00:18:45,975
you might want to make sure he's
not hungry first.

302
00:18:46,075 --> 00:18:50,342
They may hang from trees but
they sure make pathetic excuses
for monkeys.

303
00:18:52,075 --> 00:18:53,909
[Sanzo] Looks like you're out
of tricks.

304
00:18:56,709 --> 00:18:58,475
Now end this game.

305
00:18:58,575 --> 00:18:59,009
No!

306
00:18:59,109 --> 00:19:00,242
Don't shoot!

307
00:19:12,775 --> 00:19:16,542
What the hell? Why didn't you do
that from the very begining,

308
00:19:16,642 --> 00:19:18,675
instead of having to fight
them all?

309
00:19:18,809 --> 00:19:20,742
That wouldn't have
been satisfying.

310
00:19:20,842 --> 00:19:24,542
[Goku] What?
[Sanzo] For you, I mean.

311
00:19:24,642 --> 00:19:26,875
Now hurry up and finish the job.

312
00:19:27,909 --> 00:19:29,375
Listen up, ninjinka!

313
00:19:29,475 --> 00:19:32,709
You tasted like puke! Now you're
saw dust!

314
00:19:42,675 --> 00:19:43,809
Yes!

315
00:19:49,009 --> 00:19:51,609
[Gosoukan] We've been saved.

316
00:19:51,709 --> 00:19:52,909
Huh? Where am I?!

317
00:19:53,009 --> 00:19:56,742
And why is it snowing all
these crystals?

318
00:20:00,079 --> 00:20:02,420
[Gosoukan] We are
eternally grateful.

319
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:05,886
We shall be more wary of our
offerings from now on.

320
00:20:05,986 --> 00:20:07,853
[Chinpu] You have done so much
for us.

321
00:20:07,953 --> 00:20:10,386
[Mingetsu] How can we show you
our thanks?

322
00:20:10,486 --> 00:20:13,286
[Goku] You don't need to thank
us, but got any food?

323
00:20:14,586 --> 00:20:17,086
Perhaps this will meet
your approval.

324
00:20:18,553 --> 00:20:19,953
That'sll do.

325
00:20:20,886 --> 00:20:21,820
Let's move.

326
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:23,053
Sure thing!

327
00:20:25,953 --> 00:20:27,720
[Goku] Hey, Sanzo.

328
00:20:27,853 --> 00:20:28,620
[Sanzo] What is it?

329
00:20:28,720 --> 00:20:29,920
I'm sorry.

330
00:20:30,020 --> 00:20:31,520
[Sanzo] Sorry? What for?

331
00:20:31,620 --> 00:20:34,453
I'm sorry I'm such an idiot.

332
00:20:34,553 --> 00:20:37,986
[Sanzo] Don't let that bother
you. You're in good company.

333
00:20:38,086 --> 00:20:39,253
Got that right.

334
00:20:39,353 --> 00:20:40,953
We wouldn't be going on
this journey

335
00:20:41,053 --> 00:20:43,353
unless we were all a bunch
of idiots.

336
00:22:25,453 --> 00:22:28,153
[Goku] What the heck is up
with Gojyo?

337
00:22:28,253 --> 00:22:30,920
Why's he hanging around such a
little girl?

338
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:33,486
He sure is picking them young
these days.

339
00:22:33,586 --> 00:22:36,186
He seems like the type who
tends to look after people,

340
00:22:36,286 --> 00:22:39,720
then again maybe he's just
gotten himself into trouble.

341
00:22:39,820 --> 00:22:43,086
So what else is new.
"Sweet Child of Mine."

342
00:22:43,186 --> 00:22:45,120
Next time on Saiyuki.

